2.2. Stat on nb of eggs laid in function of pound type.

Code 
# Test with poisson 
library(glmmTMB)

glm1 <- glmmTMB(nbr_oeufs~1, data=CP_data, family = poisson)
glm2 <- glmmTMB(nbr_oeufs~nom, data=CP_data, family = poisson)
glm3 <- glmmTMB(nbr_oeufs~nom, data=CP_data, family = nbinom1())
glm4 <- glmmTMB(nbr_oeufs~nom + (1|replicat), data=CP_data, family = nbinom1())

AIC(glm1, glm2, glm3, glm4)

glm4  6  650.7913

# package loading 
library(readxl)

# data import 
CP_data <- read_excel("./Data/20230503_tous_replicats_choix_pondoir.xlsx") %>% mutate_if(is.character, as.factor)

BFR_data <- read_excel("./Data/20230503_tous_replicats_taux_gorgement.xlsx")

HatchingR <- read_excel("./Data/20230503_tous_replicats_oeuf_eclosion rate.xlsx")

## 2.  Choix du pondoir

2.1. Summary of data

```{r}
CP_data %>% 
  tbl_summary(include = c("nom", "index"), by = "nom",     statistic = all_continuous() ~ "Moy. : {mean}; Median: {median}; SD: {sd}")

hist(CP_data$nbr_oeufs)
summary(CP_data)

```

2.2. Stat on nb of eggs laid in function of pound type.

```{r}
# Test with poisson 
library(glmmTMB)

glm1 <- glmmTMB(nbr_oeufs~1, data=CP_data, family = poisson)
glm2 <- glmmTMB(nbr_oeufs~nom, data=CP_data, family = poisson)
glm3 <- glmmTMB(nbr_oeufs~nom, data=CP_data, family = nbinom1())
glm4 <- glmmTMB(nbr_oeufs~nom + (1|replicat), data=CP_data, family = nbinom1())

AIC(glm1, glm2, glm3, glm4)
# 3 seems better regarding AIC 
summary(glm4)

glm4%>% tbl_regression(intercept = TRUE)

emm_nbrofnR <- emmeans(glm4, pairwise~nom, infer=TRUE, type="response")
emm_nbrofnR
```

2.3. Choix du pondoir en fonction de la composition du gite d'origine des femelles 

```{r}
# choix pondoir function of origin
glmO <- glmmTMB(choix_pondoir~1, data=CP_data, family = binomial)
glma <- glmmTMB(choix_pondoir~traitement_provenance, data=CP_data, family = binomial)
glmb <- glmmTMB(choix_pondoir~traitement_provenance+(1|replicat), data=CP_data, family = binomial)

AIC(glmO,glma, glmb)

summary(glmb)
summary(glmO)
```

No choice in function of composition of breeding site origin.
